name: Faraute
description:
Esta obra es de mi serie Teriantropía.
Imaginando fusionar un búho y una figura femenina nace ella
Con ése simbolismo que caracteriza al búho y su misticismo, ella es la mensajera del misterio
Un ser taciturno que guía a quien busca el sendero de las virtudes.

This work is from my Therianthropy series.
Imagining merging an owl and a female figure she is born
With that symbolism that characterizes the owl and her mysticism, she is the messenger of the mystery
A taciturn being who guides those who seek the path of virtues.
